### Phase 2 Health
GET http://localhost:8000/api/phase2/health

### Submit beneficiary application
POST http://localhost:8000/api/phase2/beneficiary/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "national_id": "29801011234567",
  "full_name": "سارة أحمد",
  "phone": "01011111111",
  "governorate": "القاهرة",
  "city": "مدينة نصر",
  "address": "شارع النصر",
  "family_size": 6,
  "monthly_income": 1200,
  "support_type": "دعم شهري",
  "requested_amount": 3000,
  "organization_id": 1,
  "children_count": 4,
  "has_chronic_disease": true,
  "has_disability": false,
  "is_widow_or_single_mother": true,
  "rent_amount": 1800,
  "emergency_level": "MEDIUM",
  "public_case_description": "أسرة تحتاج دعم شهري للغذاء والإيجار"
}

### List admin applications scoped to Food Bank
GET http://localhost:8000/api/phase2/admin/applications?organization_id=1

### Approve application and create case
POST http://localhost:8000/api/phase2/admin/applications/APP-00001/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "decision": "APPROVED",
  "notes": "المستندات صحيحة والحالة مستحقة",
  "create_case": true,
  "required_amount": 3000,
  "case_title": "دعم شهري لأسرة محتاجة",
  "public_display_name": "أسرة محتاجة - القاهرة",
  "documents_verified": true,
  "is_monthly_case": true
}

### Donor available cases
GET http://localhost:8000/api/phase2/donor/cases?only_available=true

### Add favorite
POST http://localhost:8000/api/phase2/donor/favorites
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "case_code": "CASE-00001",
  "donor_phone": "01022222222"
}

### Donate to case
POST http://localhost:8000/api/phase2/donor/donations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "case_code": "CASE-00001",
  "donor_name": "محمد علي",
  "donor_phone": "01022222222",
  "amount": 3000,
  "payment_method": "Cash"
}

### Support profiles for charity admin
GET http://localhost:8000/api/phase2/support-profiles?organization_id=1

### Government dashboard
GET http://localhost:8000/api/phase2/government/dashboard
